  "narrative_points": [
    "In 2024-25, 111 domestic homicides were recorded in England and Wales \u2014 a fall of 5.1% on the prior year.",
    "Female victims killed by a male partner or ex-partner account for 64.0% of all domestic homicides in 2024-25 \u2014 the single largest category in the dataset, every year without exception.",
    "Murder convictions fell to 158 in 2024-25, the lowest figure in the eleven-year series, down 22.9% from 2014-15.",
    "Cases where no suspect was charged reached 134 in 2024-25 \u2014 the highest figure recorded across the same eleven years.",
    "Among victims who were acquainted with their suspect, 59.3% of homicides were sparked by quarrel, revenge, or loss of temper \u2014 not premeditation or financial motive."
  ]
